Navigation Heading Algorithm Implementation
===========================================

(Visualization tested in Chromium 62)


Quick Start - View Results
--------------------------

 - Open visualizer/index.html in a web browser.


To Run a New Test Case
----------------------

 - Change some parameters in simulator.py
    - boat starting position and heading
    - target position
    - wind speed and heading
    - beating parameter (A.K.A. p_c, which gives n)

 - Run "python2 simulator.py > visualizer/data.js"

 - View visualizer/index.html in a web browser


Overview
--------

 - heading.py - the algorithm (what we're testing)

 - simulator.py - crude simulation of boat motion

 - visualizer - crude visualization of simulation data


Notes
-----

Using the simple polar diagram. Have yet to test a more complicated one.
